file.title: AMM PART II-1285 - CHAPTER 12-21-13-03 - EMERGENCY/PARKING BRAKE HANDLE AND VALVE - SERVICING

page.data: AIRCRAFT MAINTENANCE MANUAL EMERGENCY/PARKING BRAKE HANDLE AND VALVE - SERVICING EFFECTIVITY: ALL 1. General A. The procedure for the lubrication on the Emergency/Parking Brake Handle and Roller of Emergency/Parking Brake Valve is given in AMM TASK 32-44-10-600-801-A/300.
